<https://www.gov.uk/government/people/douglas-alexander> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "Douglas Alexander was appointed Secretary of State for Scotland on 5 September 2025. He previously Minister of State at the Department for Business and Trade between 6 July 2024 and 5 September 2025, and Minister of State in the Cabinet Office between 10 February 2025 and 5 September 2025. He was elected as the MP for Lothian East in July 2024."@en .
